<tr id="L136"><td><a href="#L136">136</a></td><td>CHAPEL:  Come along, Ensign. This won't hurt. Much.</td></tr>

<tr id="L137"><td><a href="#L137">137</a></td><td>CHEKOV:  Promises.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--McCoy's office</td></tr>
<tr id="L138"><td><a href="#L138">138</a></td><td>WALLACE:  A few years ago on Aldebaran Three, my husband and I tried various carbohydrate compounds to slow down the degeneration of plant life.</td></tr>

